aptik-battery-monitor (2.0) trusty; urgency=low

  * Rotate log file when laptop is removed from charger
  * Improved readability of console output
  * Removed admin access requirement
  * Added a service for logging statistics
  * Changed logging directory to /var/log/aptik-battery-monitor
  * Renamed package, project and binaries from 'aptik-bmon' to 'aptik-battery-monitor'
  * Updated UI

